--- !u!114 &8551917545705645157
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 7442684902434093079}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5c2cac307a0fdd5419476a87cf514845, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CoffinAnim
  CoffinTop: {fileID: 2063675278219461225}
  Mummy: {fileID: 3139788791266133402}
  Door: {fileID: 0}
  RiddleTextMesh: {fileID: 0}
  DoorOpenClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1db53b31e2bff8444854ed416a6484ba, type: 3}
  CoffinMoveClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 6a832ac30e7265a4099847be7cdec999, type: 3}
  CartoonClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5a1b59b5df73b6d48a8132b41733c649, type: 3}
  IntroClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 46b5370f526e1ab45966620b026a24c5, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 048ab21a27b72d7498794fbb37417374, type: 3}
  RiddleClips:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 18de0aa6e68f15d49b4c2d46da9032dd, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 35888fb3e2e8f684299df5ffe8e03da2, type: 3}
  IntroTexts:
  - "Who dares to disturb my slumber when I have slept for thousands of years?! This
    will be punished. A riddle will be told, if answered correctly all of you are
    free to go, wrong answer and you will have to stay here forever. One of the objects
    you have collected in one of my puzzles will answer the riddle. Place the object
    you have chosen on the table in front of you and see if you have chosen the correct
    one\u2026."
  - "Vem v\xE5gar att st\xF6ra min s\xF6mn n\xE4r jag sovit i flera tusen \xE5r!!!!!
    Detta kommer att bli straffat. Jag kommer ge er en g\xE5ta, om ni svarar r\xE4tt
    \xE4r ni alla fria att g\xE5, svarar ni fel s\xE5 f\xF6rlorar en av er visionen.
    Vem det blir \xE5terst\xE5r att se, svara s\xE5 f\xE5r vi se. "
  RiddleTexts:
  - 'I am always near, but never far.\nI am always around, but never seen.\nI am
    often avoided, but I always catch up.\nI will come when your old and grey, or
    maybe even the very next day.\nI will come with cold embrace, and give you rest
    with a chill kiss on your face.\nI come in many forms whether it''s irony, love,
    laughter, or hate.\nI am everyone''s final fate. '
  - "Jag f\xF6ljer dig varje \\ndag, men du kan aldrig springa ifr\xE5n mig. \\nJag
    syns aldrig med \xF6gon, men alla vet att jag finns. \\nVissa m\xF6ter mig n\xE4r
    de \xE4r v\xE4ldigt gamla, andra mycket tidigare. \\nIngen vill tr\xE4ffa mig,
    men alla g\xF6r det n\xE5gon g\xE5ng. \\nVad \xE4r jag?"
  OnAnswerCorrect:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  OnAnswerWrong:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
